      "content": "At the core of Powerhouse's approach is a belief in structured decentralization. Powerhouse enables independent teams to coordinate around shared goals, using workflows encoded in software rather than enforced by hierarchy. Contributors take ownership over workstreams, reputations are built over time, and budgets are allocated based on transparent processes. This is not decentralization for its own sake -- it is a functional reimagining of how work gets done at scale.",
